<!--
  Acknowledges two one-time schema changes in this deploy:

  1. indexing-change: nip05 / lud16 / website go from `summary` to
     `index | summary` so they become searchable (docs/search-vs-tapestry.md
     §8.4/§9). Reindexed for existing docs via the kind-0 re-feed
     (scripts/refeed_kind0_to_vespa.py).

