     deprecated alias of `name`, so ingest now folds it into `name` and we no
     longer store it as its own field. Only needed on environments where the
     P1 `username` field was already deployed; harmless elsewhere.

  `until` MUST be within 30 days of the deploy date. Remove this file (or let it
  expire) once the changes have been activated everywhere — it should NOT
  linger, or it would silently allow future accidental schema changes.
-->
<validation-overrides>
    <allow until="2026-07-14">indexing-change</allow>
    <allow until="2026-07-14">field-removal</allow>
</validation-overrides>